\v 11 Depois, <a name="01400401100004">fez</a> <a name="01400401100006">Hirão</a> as <a name="01400401100012" ll="SDBH:סִיר:000000" il="Bolen00037;NBGmk20140119h">panelas</a>, e as <a name="01400401100020" ll="SDBH:יָע:000000">pás</a>, e as <a name="01400401100028" ll="SDBH:מִזְרָק:000000">bacias</a>. Assim, <a name="01400401100032" ll="SDBH:כלה:000001">terminou</a> <a name="01400401100034;01400401100036" ll="SDBH:חִירָם:000001;SDBH:חוּרָם:000002">ele</a> de <a name="01400401100040">fazer</a> a <a name="01400401100046" ll="SDBH:מְלָאכָה:000000">obra</a> para o <a name="01400401100056" ll="SDBH:מֶלֶךְ:000000">rei</a> <a name="01400401100058" ll="SDBH:שְׁלֹמֹה:000000">Salomão</a>, para a <a name="01400401100062" ll="SDBH:בַּיִת:000000" il="HK00232;LB00235;NBGbs20090430-1_87;NBGbs20110223-127;NBGmk20120826;NBGmk20120826a;NBGmk20140917">Casa</a> de <a name="01400401100066" ll="SDBH:אֱלֹהִים:000002">Deus</a>: 
