\v 17 Quanto a ti, se <a name="01400701700008" ll="SDBH:הלך:000004">andares</a> <a name="01400701700012">diante</a> <a name="01400701700012">de</a> <a name="01400701700012">mim</a>, como <a name="01400701700018" ll="SDBH:הלך:000004">andou</a> <a name="01400701700020" ll="SDBH:דָּוִד:000000">Davi</a>, <a name="01400701700022" ll="SDBH:אָב:000000">teu</a> <a name="01400701700022" ll="SDBH:אָב:000000">pai</a>, e <a name="01400701700028">fizeres</a> segundo tudo o que <a name="01400701700036" ll="SDBH:צוה:000000">te</a> <a name="01400701700036" ll="SDBH:צוה:000000">ordenei</a>, e <a name="01400701700046" ll="SDBH:שׁמר:000003">guardares</a> os <a name="01400701700040" ll="SDBH:חֹק:000002">meus</a> <a name="01400701700040" ll="SDBH:חֹק:000002">estatutos</a> e os <a name="01400701700044" ll="SDBH:מִשְׁפָּט:000006">meus</a> <a name="01400701700044" ll="SDBH:מִשְׁפָּט:000006">juízos</a>, 
