\v 19 Porém, se vós <a name="01400701900006" ll="SDBH:שׁוב:000026">vos</a> <a name="01400701900006" ll="SDBH:שׁוב:000026">desviardes</a>, e <a name="01400701900012" ll="SDBH:עזב:000006">deixardes</a> os <a name="01400701900014" ll="SDBH:חֻקָּה:000001">meus</a> <a name="01400701900014" ll="SDBH:חֻקָּה:000001">estatutos</a> e os <a name="01400701900018" ll="SDBH:מִצְוָה:000000">meus</a> <a name="01400701900018" ll="SDBH:מִצְוָה:000000">mandamentos</a>, que vos <a name="01400701900022">prescrevi</a>, e <a name="01400701900030" ll="SDBH:הלך:000004">fordes</a>, e <a name="01400701900034" ll="SDBH:עבד:000002">servirdes</a> a <a name="01400701900038" ll="SDBH:אַחֵר:000000">outros</a> <a name="01400701900036" ll="SDBH:אֱלֹהִים:000000">deuses</a>, e <a name="01400701900042" ll="SDBH:חוה:001000" il="Prostrate_figures">os</a> <a name="01400701900042" ll="SDBH:חוה:001000" il="Prostrate_figures">adorardes</a>, 
