\v 7 Naquele <a name="01401600700008" ll="SDBH:עֵת:000000">tempo</a>, <a name="01401600700014">veio</a> <a name="01401600700016;01401600700020" ll="SDBH:חֲנָנִי:000000;SDBH:רֹאֶה:000000">Hanani</a> a <a name="01401600700024" ll="SDBH:אָסָא:000000">Asa</a>, <a name="01401600700026" ll="SDBH:מֶלֶךְ:000000">rei</a> de <a name="01401600700028" ll="SDBH:יְהוּדָה:000000">Judá</a>, e lhe <a name="01401600700032" ll="SDBH:אמר:000000">disse</a>: Porquanto <a name="01401600700038" ll="SDBH:שׁען:000001">confiaste</a> no <a name="01401600700042" ll="SDBH:מֶלֶךְ:000000">rei</a> da <a name="01401600700044" ll="SDBH:אֲרָם:000001" il="adr1306212718">Síria</a> e não <a name="01401600700050" ll="SDBH:שׁען:000001">confiaste</a> no <a name="01401600700054" ll="SDBH:יהוה:000000">Senhor</a>, <a name="01401600700056" ll="SDBH:אֱלֹהִים:000001">teu</a> <a name="01401600700056" ll="SDBH:אֱלֹהִים:000001">Deus</a>, o exército do <a name="01401600700066" ll="SDBH:מֶלֶךְ:000000" tl="HOTTP1618">rei</a> <a name="01401600700068" ll="SDBH:אֲרָם:000001" il="adr1306212718" tl="HOTTP1618">da</a> <a name="01401600700068" ll="SDBH:אֲרָם:000001" il="adr1306212718" tl="HOTTP1618">Síria</a> <a name="01401600700062" ll="SDBH:מלט:000000">escapou</a> das <a name="01401600700072">tuas</a> <a name="01401600700072">mãos</a>. 
\v 8 Acaso, não foram os <a name="01401600800008" ll="SDBH:כּוּשִׁי:000000" il="Camels_in_Ethiopia_02">etíopes</a> e os <a name="01401600800014" ll="SDBH:לוּב:000000" il="Libya_BMNG">líbios</a> <a name="01401600800024" ll="SDBH:רֹב:000000">grande</a> <a name="01401600800020" ll="SDBH:חַיִל:000002" il="HK00197;LB00198;NBGmk20131008a;adr1603195037">exército</a>, com <a name="01401600800038;01401600800040" ll="SDBH:מְאֹד:000001">muitíssimos</a> <a name="01401600800028" ll="SDBH:רֶכֶב:001001">carros</a> e <a name="01401600800034">cavaleiros</a>? Porém, <a name="01401600800046" ll="SDBH:שׁען:000001">tendo</a> <a name="01401600800046" ll="SDBH:שׁען:000001">tu</a> <a name="01401600800046" ll="SDBH:שׁען:000001">confiado</a> no <a name="01401600800050">Senhor</a>, <a name="01401600800052">ele</a> <a name="01401600800052">os</a> <a name="01401600800052">entregou</a> nas <a name="01401600800056">tuas</a> <a name="01401600800056">mãos</a>. 
\v 9 Porque, quanto ao <a name="01401600900004" ll="SDBH:יהוה:000000">Senhor</a>, <a name="01401600900006" ll="SDBH:עַיִן:000000">seus</a> <a name="01401600900006" ll="SDBH:עַיִן:000000">olhos</a> <a name="01401600900008" ll="SDBH:שׁוט:000000">passam</a> por toda a <a name="01401600900016" ll="SDBH:אֶרֶץ:000000">terra</a>, para <a name="01401600900020" ll="SDBH:חזק:000001">mostrar</a>-<a name="01401600900020" ll="SDBH:חזק:000001">se</a> <a name="01401600900020" ll="SDBH:חזק:000001">forte</a> para com aqueles <a name="01401600900024" ll="SDBH:לֵבָב:000001">cujo</a> <a name="01401600900024" ll="SDBH:לֵבָב:000001">coração</a> é <a name="01401600900026" ll="SDBH:שָׁלֵם:000003">totalmente</a> dele; nisto <a name="01401600900030" ll="SDBH:סכל:000000">procedeste</a> <a name="01401600900030" ll="SDBH:סכל:000000">loucamente</a>; por isso, desde <a name="01401600900040">agora</a>, <a name="01401600900042">haverá</a> <a name="01401600900046" ll="SDBH:מִלְחָמָה:000000">guerras</a> contra ti. 
\v 10 Porém <a name="01401601000006" ll="SDBH:אָסָא:000000">Asa</a> <a name="01401601000004" ll="SDBH:כעס:000000">se</a> <a name="01401601000004" ll="SDBH:כעס:000000">indignou</a> contra o <a name="01401601000012" ll="SDBH:רֹאֶה:000000">vidente</a> e <a name="01401601000016">o</a> <a name="01401601000016">lançou</a> no <a name="01401601000018" ll="SDBH:בַּיִת:000000" il="HK00232;LB00235;NBGbs20090430-1_87;NBGbs20110223-127;NBGmk20120826;NBGmk20120826a;NBGmk20140917">cárcere</a>, no <a name="01401601000022" ll="SDBH:מַהְפֶּכֶת:000001">tronco</a>, porque <a name="01401601000028" ll="SDBH:זַעַף:000000">se</a> <a name="01401601000028" ll="SDBH:זַעַף:000000">enfurecera</a> contra ele por causa disso; na mesma <a name="01401601000052" ll="SDBH:עֵת:000000">ocasião</a>, <a name="01401601000038" ll="SDBH:רצץ:000002">oprimiu</a> <a name="01401601000040" ll="SDBH:אָסָא:000000">Asa</a> alguns do <a name="01401601000046" ll="SDBH:עַם:000000">povo</a>.
    
\v 11 Eis que os mais <a name="01401601100006" ll="SDBH:דָּבָר:000002">atos</a> de <a name="01401601100008" ll="SDBH:אָסָא:000000">Asa</a>, tanto os <a name="01401601100012" ll="SDBH:רִאשֹׁון:000000">primeiros</a> como os <a name="01401601100018" ll="SDBH:אַחֲרֹון:000001">últimos</a>, estão <a name="01401601100022" ll="SDBH:כתב:000000" il="Scribe at work;WritingScroll-ReedPen-01-065d;tb032014452">escritos</a> no <a name="01401601100026" ll="SDBH:סֵפֶר:000006">Livro</a> da História dos <a name="01401601100030" ll="SDBH:מֶלֶךְ:000000">Reis</a> de <a name="01401601100034" ll="SDBH:יְהוּדָה:000000">Judá</a> e <a name="01401601100038" ll="SDBH:יִשְׂרָאֵל:000000">Israel</a>. 
