name="01402201100096">de</a> <a name="01402201100098" ll="SDBH:עֲתַלְיָה:000000">Atalia</a>, e não <a name="01402201100104" ll="SDBH:מות:000001">foi</a> <a name="01402201100104" ll="SDBH:מות:000001">morto</a>. 
\v 12 Joás <a name="01402201200016" ll="SDBH:חבא:001000">esteve</a> com eles <a name="01402201200018" ll="SDBH:שֵׁשׁ:000000">seis</a> <a name="01402201200020" ll="SDBH:שָׁנָה:000000">anos</a> na <a name="01402201200010" ll="SDBH:בַּיִת:000000" il="HK00232;LB00235;NBGbs20090430-1_87;NBGbs20110223-127;NBGmk20120826;NBGmk20120826a;NBGmk20140917">Casa</a> de <a name="01402201200014" ll="SDBH:אֱלֹהִים:000002">Deus</a>, e <a name="01402201200024" ll="SDBH:עֲתַלְיָה:000000">Atalia</a> <a name="01402201200026" ll="SDBH:מלך:000000">reinou</a> no <a name="01402201200032" ll="SDBH:אֶרֶץ:000000">país</a>.
