\v 3 Toda essa <a name="01402300300010" ll="SDBH:קָהָל:000000">congregação</a> <a name="01402300300004" ll="SDBH:כרת:000001">fez</a> <a name="01402300300012" ll="SDBH:בְּרִית:000000" il="Treaty_of_Kadesh">aliança</a> com o <a name="01402300300026" ll="SDBH:מֶלֶךְ:000000">rei</a> na <a name="01402300300016" ll="SDBH:בַּיִת:000000" il="HK00232;LB00235;NBGbs20090430-1_87;NBGbs20110223-127;NBGmk20120826;NBGmk20120826a;NBGmk20140917">Casa</a> de <a name="01402300300020" ll="SDBH:אֱלֹהִים:000002">Deus</a>; e Joiada lhes <a name="01402300300030" ll="SDBH:אמר:000000">disse</a>: Eis que <a name="01402300300042" ll="SDBH:מלך:000000">reinará</a> o <a name="01402300300036" ll="SDBH:בֵּן:000000">filho</a> do <a name="01402300300040" ll="SDBH:מֶלֶךְ:000000">rei</a>, como <a name="01402300300048" ll="SDBH:דבר:001000">falou</a> o <a name="01402300300050" ll="SDBH:יהוה:000000">Senhor</a> a respeito dos <a name="01402300300054" ll="SDBH:בֵּן:000000">filhos</a> de <a name="01402300300056" ll="SDBH:דָּוִד:000000">Davi</a>. 
\v 4 Esta é a <a name="01402300400006" ll="SDBH:דָּבָר:000002">obra</a> que <a name="01402300400010">haveis</a> <a name="01402300400010">de</a> <a name="01402300400010">fazer</a>: uma <a name="01402300400014" ll="SDBH:שְׁלִישִׁי:000001">terça</a> <a name="01402300400014" ll="SDBH:שְׁלִישִׁי:000001">parte</a> de vós, <a name="01402300400028" ll="SDBH:כֹּהֵן:000000" il="LB00263">sacerdotes</a> e <a name="01402300400036" ll="SDBH:לֵוִי:000001">levitas</a>, que <a name="01402300400018">entrais</a> no <a name="01402300400022" ll="SDBH:שַׁבָּת:000000">sábado</a>, servirá de <a name="01402300400040" ll="SDBH:שֹׁועֵר:000000">guardas</a> da <a name="01402300400044" ll="SDBH:סַף:001000" il="Realia:3.1.2.6b">porta</a>; 
