\v 6 Porém ninguém <a name="01402300600006">entre</a> na <a name="01402300600008" ll="SDBH:בַּיִת:000000" il="HK00232;HK00245;LB00235;NBGbs20090430-1_87;NBGbs20110223-127;NBGlo20140606;NBGlo20140606b;NBGlo20140708c;NBGlo20140825;NBGmk20120826;NBGmk20120826a;NBGmk20140917;jlm_sol_complex_ann;jlm_soltemp_altar_m01;jlm_soltemp_d01;jlm_soltemp_m06;jlm_soltemp_pillars_m01">Casa</a> <a name="01402300600010" ll="SDBH:יהוה:000000">do</a> <a name="01402300600010" ll="SDBH:יהוה:000000">Senhor</a>, senão os <a name="01402300600018" ll="SDBH:כֹּהֵן:000000" il="LB00263">sacerdotes</a> e os <a name="01402300600030" ll="SDBH:לֵוִי:000001">levitas</a> que <a name="01402300600024" ll="SDBH:שׁרת:000001">ministram</a>; estes <a name="01402300600034">entrarão</a>, porque são <a name="01402300600038" ll="SDBH:קֹדֶשׁ:000001">santos</a>; mas todo o <a name="01402300600048">povo</a> <a name="01402300600050" ll="SDBH:שׁמר:000003">guardará</a> o <a name="01402300600052" ll="SDBH:מִשְׁמֶרֶת:000004">preceito</a> do <a name="01402300600054">Senhor</a>. 
