\v 4 <a name="01402600400004">Ele</a> <a name="01402600400004">fez</a> o que era <a name="01402600400008" ll="SDBH:יָשָׁר:000003">reto</a> <a name="01402600400012" ll="SDBH:עַיִן:000000">perante</a> o <a name="01402600400014" ll="SDBH:יהוה:000000">Senhor</a>, segundo tudo o que <a name="01402600400022">fizera</a> <a name="01402600400024" ll="SDBH:אֲמַצְיָה:000000">Amazias</a>, <a name="01402600400026" ll="SDBH:אָב:000000">seu</a> <a name="01402600400026" ll="SDBH:אָב:000000">pai</a>. 
\v 5 Propôs-se <a name="01402600500008" ll="SDBH:דרשׁ:000003">buscar</a> a <a name="01402600500010" ll="SDBH:אֱלֹהִים:000002">Deus</a> nos <a name="01402600500014" ll="SDBH:יֹום:000003">dias</a> de <a name="01402600500016" ll="SDBH:זְכַרְיָהוּ:000009">Zacarias</a>, que era <a name="01402600500020" ll="SDBH:בין:000003">sábio</a> nas <a name="01402600500024" ll="SDBH:ראה:000000" tl="HOTTP1646">visões</a> de <a name="01402600500028" ll="SDBH:אֱלֹהִים:000002" tl="HOTTP1646">Deus</a>; nos <a name="01402600500034" ll="SDBH:יֹום:000003">dias</a> em que <a name="01402600500036" ll="SDBH:דרשׁ:000003">buscou</a> ao <a name="01402600500040" ll="SDBH:יהוה:000000">Senhor</a>, <a name="01402600500046" ll="SDBH:אֱלֹהִים:000002">Deus</a> <a name="01402600500042" ll="SDBH:צלח:001005">o</a> <a name="01402600500042" ll="SDBH:צלח:001005">fez</a> <a name="01402600500042" ll="SDBH:צלח:001005">prosperar</a>.
    
