0070" ll="SDBH:חוּץ:000000;SDBH:יצא:000001" il="HK00169;Realia:3.13.2;tb052001215">fora</a>, ao <a name="01402901600066" ll="SDBH:נַחַל:000000" il="NBGbs20090428-1_39;tb110603119">ribeiro</a> <a name="01402901600068" ll="SDBH:קִדְרֹון:000000" il="NBGbs20090227-1-3;NBGbs20090227-1_34">de</a> <a name="01402901600068" ll="SDBH:קִדְרֹון:000000" il="NBGbs20090227-1-3;NBGbs20090227-1_34">Cedrom</a>. 
