\v 34 Os <a name="01402903400006" ll="SDBH:כֹּהֵן:000000" il="LB00263">sacerdotes</a>, porém, eram mui <a name="01402903400012" ll="SDBH:מְעַט:000000">poucos</a> e não <a name="01402903400018" ll="SDBH:יכל:000000">podiam</a> <a name="01402903400022" ll="SDBH:פשׁט:000001">esfolar</a> a todos os <a name="01402903400030" ll="SDBH:עֹלָה:000000" il="HK00251;HK00256;LB00253;LB00254;LB00255;NBGlo20140504a;NBGlo20140504b;NBGlo20140504c;Realia:4.2.3">holocaustos</a>; pelo que <a name="01402903400036" ll="SDBH:אָח:000002">seus</a> <a name="01402903400036" ll="SDBH:אָח:000002">irmãos</a>, os <a name="01402903400040" ll="SDBH:לֵוִי:000001">levitas</a>, <a name="01402903400034" ll="SDBH:חזק:000002">os</a> <a name="01402903400034" ll="SDBH:חזק:000002">ajudaram</a>, até <a name="01402903400044" ll="SDBH:כלה:000000">findar</a>-se a <a name="01402903400048" ll="SDBH:מְלָאכָה:000000">obra</a> e até que os outros <a name="01402903400058" ll="SDBH:כֹּהֵן:000000" il="LB00263">sacerdotes</a> <a name="01402903400054" ll="SDBH:קדשׁ:000003">se</a> <a name="01402903400054" ll="SDBH:קדשׁ:000003">santificaram</a>; porque os <a name="01402903400064" ll="SDBH:לֵוִי:000001">levitas</a> foram <a name="01402903400074;01402903400076">mais</a> <a name="01402903400066" ll="SDBH:יָשָׁר:000004">retos</a> de <a name="01402903400068" ll="SDBH:לֵבָב:000001">coração</a>, para se <a name="01402903400072" ll="SDBH:קדשׁ:000003">santificarem</a>, do <a name="01402903400074;01402903400076">que</a> <a name="01402903400074;01402903400076">os</a> <a name="01402903400078" ll="SDBH:כֹּהֵן:000000" il="LB00263">sacerdotes</a>. 
